    "body": "### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nany\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nany\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nall\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nany\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ndefault\n\n### Installation\n\nany\n\n### How to reproduce the issue\n\nset sj=-100 \n\n### Expected behavior\n\nscroll full page and set cursor top\n\n### Actual behavior\n\nscroll half page and set cursor on center buffer.\r\n\r\nNot work propetly in Nvim and Vim. \r\n\r\nTrying set scroll to page flip (emacs default behavior), cursor set in center page and scroll half page. \r\n\r\nin Vim opened issue, but who cares... https://github.com/vim/vim/issues/1527",
